data.description: Don’t miss this unique Estates home boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, 2 car garage, complete with a stunning saltwater pool and a 2,400 sq ft Red Iron Metal building/workshop nestled on 2.27 acres. Live comfortably with the split floor plan with ceramic tile flooring in the living spaces and vinyl flooring in the bedrooms. The roof was replaced in 2017, A/C system in 2018, RO system for whole house was installed in 2021, and washer & dryer in 2019. French doors lead you to a large paver deck w/screened lanai, showcasing a beautiful saltwater pool. Alongside this home, a 40x60 2,400 sq ft Red Iron metal building/workshop awaits, ideal for business owners or car enthusiasts. Equipped with electricity, two 10x10 roll down doors, a 12x12' roll down door, a 9,000 LB car lift, plus an enclosed office space. The meticulously landscaped & fully cleared yard is fenced on two sides, featuring palms, fruit trees, and a serene pond. An additional fully fenced in yard space on the side offers freedom for your pets to roam. Boasting TWO distinct driveways- a paved one leading to the home and another to the rear workshop- making it an ideal haven for both residential and business owners.
